AREAS FOR IMPROVEMENT

**Material organization**: Need to do a deep clean of Practical Life area. Some trays are grimy. Missing pieces.

**Language materials**: Could use more small objects for word building. Running low.

**Transitions**: Some kids struggling with choosing work independently. May need to do a group lesson on "how to choose work."

**Social dynamics**: Noah and Leo keep gravitating toward same materials. Need to observe this pattern - are they actually friends or just competitive? May need to seat them apart at circle time.

