CONCERNS

**One concern**: Leo (4.5) seems to be avoiding practical life work. Always chooses sensorial or tries to get to math materials. May need to guide him back to some practical life exercises to build those skills too. Can't skip areas.

**Another concern**: Mia is doing great with letters but struggling with social interactions. Tends to work alone, doesn't join group activities willingly. Need to watch this - academic skills developing but social-emotional may need support.

